            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>What's New in 2.4.0</h2>
                    <h3>In-app auto-updates are here</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Sparkle is now integrated into the app — future updates download and install in place</li>
                        <li>New "Check for Updates…" item in the time.md menu</li>
                        <li>Updates are signed with an ED25519 key and verified before installation</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>This is the first release with Sparkle linked. Once you're on 2.4.0, every later release will be offered to you automatically.</p>
